Thank you. I am
Cardinal Mancini.

141
00:07:03,690 --> 00:07:06,057
Hi. This is Agent Hayes
and Agent Larson...

142
00:07:06,793 --> 00:07:08,659
How you doing? From
the Secret Service.

143
00:07:08,728 --> 00:07:10,959
Cool. You know why we're here?

144
00:07:11,464 --> 00:07:13,660
Uh... Yeah, no.

145
