the UN this afternoon.

146
00:07:17,737 --> 00:07:21,230
Right, the Pope is addressing
the... Right. Yeah, I remember.

147
00:07:21,841 --> 00:07:24,333
Ah, yes. And as
papal security liaison,

148
00:07:24,411 --> 00:07:28,246
