emergency, God forbid.

150
00:07:30,717 --> 00:07:34,745
Sure. Great. Well, I'm happy to
help. You need the presidential bay?

151
00:07:35,021 --> 00:07:36,232
Yes, sir. And
surrounding floors.

152
00:07:36,256 --> 00:07:38,225
Ah, yes. And the
surrounding floors.

153
00:07:39,826 --> 00:07:42,193
Well, I don't love the
sound of surrounding floors.

154
00:07:42,262 --> 00:07:44,254
This is a working hospital.

155
00:07:44,864 --> 00:07:46,504
It's a precaution.
And merely a formality.

156
