Before we let her rip I need to make
sure that you're absolutely certain

167
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:28,079
that you wanna end
your chemotherapy.

168
00:08:28,241 --> 00:08:29,937
Never more sure of anything.

169
00:08:31,644 --> 00:08:35,411
Okay. Well, while we wait for your
records to be sent over from Baptist,

170
00:08:35,482 --> 00:08:37,560
we can schedule the procedure,
and then we'll take it from...

