Dr. Sharpe. Lila,
I'm with a patient.

172
00:08:38,985 --> 00:08:40,096
I'm sorry. I tried to tell them.

173
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,918
Tell who? Yeah, she's the one.

174
00:08:41,988 --> 00:08:43,908
Ma'am, I'm gonna have
to ask you a few questions.

175
00:08:44,724 --> 00:08:46,235
I haven't done anything.
Don't you touch her!

176
00:08:46,259 --> 00:08:47,591
Sheila! Come on, let's go.

177
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:48,871
Sorry. Excuse me.
What's going on, please?

178
00:08:48,895 --> 00:08:52,332
Hi. I'm Carl Jimenez. I'm
Mr. Brandt's legal guardian.

179
00:08:52,966 --> 00:08:54,229
That woman kidnapped him.

180
00:09:00,407 --> 00:09:01,431
Gentlemen.

181
00:09:01,608 --> 00:09:03,440
