This morning in chemo.

325
00:16:34,527 --> 00:16:37,224
Everyone was laughing, and
I could have done something.

326
00:16:37,296 --> 00:16:39,788
I could have gotten someone.

327
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:42,362
She was laughing
at her symptoms.

328
00:16:42,702 --> 00:16:46,434
She was laughing because
of her symptoms, Max.

329
00:16:48,975 --> 00:16:50,068
There's a difference.

330
