but I rarely use email.

337
00:17:16,602 --> 00:17:18,662
Honestly, I thought it
was a passing trend.

338
00:17:19,605 --> 00:17:20,800
What do you use?

339
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:23,300
A cup of tea and a conversation.

340
00:17:25,745 --> 00:17:28,305
Is it your back
that's bothering you?

341
00:17:29,081 --> 00:17:30,105
Maybe I can help.

342
00:17:30,850 --> 00:17:33,285
You wanna help?
Remember your password.

343
00:17:34,487 --> 00:17:36,183
Hello, John Wilkes Booth.

344
00:17:36,689 --> 00:17:38,317
I warned you not
to do it, didn't I? Ah.

345
00:17:38,424 --> 00:17:39,983
You did?

346
00:17:40,092 --> 00:17:41,932
Yeah. Hell yeah, I did,
because it was idiotic.

347
00:17:42,628 --> 00:17:45,507
You mean you knew about this little
stunt and you decided not to report it?

348
00:17:45,531 --> 00:17:46,863
Yeah. No.

349
00:17:47,166 --> 00:17:48,691
No, wait. What?

350
00:17:49,268 --> 00:17:50,292
Take a seat, please.

