postpartum hemorrhaging,

439
00:23:16,662 --> 00:23:18,702
which is the number one
cause of maternal mortality?

440
00:23:21,033 --> 00:23:23,127
Not a joke.

441
00:23:23,335 --> 00:23:24,860
Max... What?

442
00:23:25,971 --> 00:23:29,533
Rest assured that
hemorrhaging is very rare, okay?

443
00:23:29,642 --> 00:23:32,373
Yeah, rare, but 5% of births
and double that for Cesareans

444
00:23:32,478 --> 00:23:34,208
and I mean, if mom
does have a headache,

445
00:23:34,313 --> 00:23:35,857
that could be preeclampsia
or any number of...

446
00:23:35,881 --> 00:23:38,009
Max, stop it. Sorry, sorry.

