Jimmy until the Medicaid kicks in.

455
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:06,638
As long as Jimmy's okay.
That's what's important.

456
00:24:07,546 --> 00:24:08,570
Where is he?

457
00:24:22,194 --> 00:24:23,355
Jimmy couldn't have gone far.

458
00:24:23,429 --> 00:24:25,489
Sepsis in oncology,
missing patients...

459
00:24:25,564 --> 00:24:27,604
This isn't supposed to happen
here at New Amsterdam.

460
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:30,329
Well, it's still a hospital, Max.
People get sick, scared or...

